Also spaces and hyphens are allowed multiple times. So we ignore spaces and hyphens when checking duplicates. Also maybe other whitespace? Only spaces and hyphens allowed to appear multiple times. So we should skip bytes that are ASCII space (0x20) and hyphen (0x2D). Also maybe other punctuation? Not needed.

